On Thu, Aug 9, 2012 at 3:14 PM, Mark Baker &lt;distobj@...&gt; wrote:

&gt; **
&gt;
&gt; That&#39;s not self-descriptive, it&#39;s just &quot;descriptive&quot;.
&gt;
